{"tid":1621261,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【今晚九時「臨時禁制令」申請開庭】","createTime":"2019-10-04T12:58:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T13:58:08.000Z","uid":114928,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"2cc1ca29b04f160aeea20afb2c3cac743e839582","tid":1621261,"uid":114928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T12:58:31.000Z","msg":"【今晚九時「臨時禁制令」申請開庭】<br />\n<br />\n就林鄭月娥及行政會議成員根據香港法例第241章《緊急情況規例條例》而實施的《禁止蒙面規例》一事，岑敖暉於下午已正式向法庭提出司法覆核申請。相關審訊詳情仍有待司法機關方面通知，相信要等一段時間才能開庭處理。<br />\n<br />\n由於《禁止蒙面規例》對港人的基本權利和自由構成嚴重的威脅和限制，一旦生效，對港人權利和自由會構成不可逆轉的傷害。<br />\n<br />\n故此，岑已經正式申請臨時禁制令，要求法庭儘快頒下命令，禁止《禁止蒙面規例》於午夜後生效。案件將於九點於高等法院開庭。"},{"pid":"5d25dbb4bc9a0cd60d26bde821e1a166c6fc18d2","tid":1621261,"uid":175159,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T13:02:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ay2K1g9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fay2K1g9.jpg&h=51c7d7e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RGL1i3P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRGL1i3P.jpg&h=e0c062dd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2MTqLJQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2MTqLJQ.jpg&h=b3c0b4bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc095473d657dcd5fa31a9e0c34104d4f77e98e3","tid":1621261,"uid":17711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T13:06:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"467983b14867400c9c458af7c9161dc477acf041","tid":1621261,"uid":46560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T13:07:00.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"5aaca033e4b86ddaeb511628564fb4397c695cb1","tid":1621261,"uid":258403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T13:07:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b67b5cafec1645bf289865ba18fdd1176744e203","tid":1621261,"uid":46560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T13:08:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d71bc0ead1fd3e5e6e6f4909f5e8